- Breakout sysfs file and directory management into seperate file in order
  to reduce duplication of code and have consistent error checking.

  Example API:

  - sysfs.c
    - sysfs_open
    - sysfs_close
    - sysfs_write
    - sysfs_read
    - sysfs_valid
  
- SPI Support
- I2C Support
- ADC Support
